print("Features:")
print("  🔫 Infinite Ammo (Ammo, MaxAmmo)")
print("  🛡️ Infinite Durability (Durability, MaxDurability)")
print("  🔍 Auto-detect new tools")
print("  ⚡ Real-time scanning")
print("  📦 Scan Backpack + Character")
print("\nPress [K] to toggle")
